text_en:
The doctor gave me affection
not only as a scientist,
but as a person.{END}

…I was an orphan,
and I thought of him
almost as a father…{END}

Even after I left
the doctor's side,
I kept in touch with him…{END}

…I wanted to complete
my research… my dream…
no matter what…{END}

I thought I would not care
even if I had to sell my soul
to do it…{END}

The other one there…
You are the rumored…
Kamen Rider, are you not?{END}

If we do not stop him… Jagan,
humanity's future will change…
it will vanish!{END}

It can transfer matter
between the eras
where the device exists.{END}

However, only matter can transfer…
likely only those with bodies
that are not living flesh…{END}

But if this space…
if he is destroyed,
that matter will return
to its original era…{END}

Furthermore, I do not know
what effects the collapse
of this space may cause…{END}

If we can stop Jagan,
I will not mourn the memories here…
not even memories of fighting evil!{END}

…Understood…
If we use all the power
in this plant,{END}

Only once… After that,
it depends on whether this device holds
or he is destroyed…{END}

! But if you do that,
the device…
your life, Doctor!{END}

…It is all right…
Through this device, I saw it…
my own future…{END}

All of the sins I committed…
And I can no longer…
return to being human…{END}

Now, activate this device.
…Only you can do it…
Please, Yuki…{END}

That created a distortion
in me as a person and as a scientist…
just like this space…{END}
